<h2 class="bold font-l">Rorschach's Calling Card</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Rorschach leaves his calling card with two tied-up criminals. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CallingCard" class='trope-example-link'>Calling Card</a></p>
